docs {
  # Get Comprehensive Insights
  
  Returns a complete dashboard of business intelligence and analytics including:
  - Sales performance metrics
  - Customer analytics and segmentation
  - Revenue analytics and KPIs
  - Order fulfillment metrics
  - Inventory health
  - Growth metrics (MoM comparisons)
  - Payment analysis
  
  ## Industry Standard Metrics Included:
  - Customer Lifetime Value (CLV)
  - Month-over-Month Growth Rate
  - Average Order Value (AOV)
  - Collection Rate
  - Inventory Turnover
  - Customer Segmentation Analysis
  
  ## Query Parameters:
  - `startDate` (optional): Filter data from this date (YYYY-MM-DD)
  - `endDate` (optional): Filter data until this date (YYYY-MM-DD)
  - `compareWithPrevious` (optional): Compare with previous period
}
